Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}氣候管理，節約能源{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Climate controlled stacks, energy efficient,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}整個收藏可能  可以都塞進電子書內{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}now mind you the whole collection  could probably fit on a Kindle,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,0:01:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不過至少學生們  又多了個躲雨的地方{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but at least the cadets will have  another place to get out of the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你有參與設計嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Did you have much input on the design?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}藍圖有經過我的認可{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I approved the blue prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:02:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果要簽上我的名字  就必須保證蓋得很好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If something's gonna have my name on it,  I want to make damn sure they build it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我老公大概自以為是建築師吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think my husband fancies himself a bit  of an architect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}傑弗遜設計了蒙蒂塞洛…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, Jefferson designed Monticello...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他也跟自己的奴隸上床{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He also fucked his slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}幸好我沒有奴隸{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Luckily I don't have any,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}所以這種誘惑還沒出現{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}so that particular temptation  hasn't presented itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}山特諾  南卡羅來納州第一軍事學院{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The Sentinel,  South Carolina's premiere military college.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}教會我榮譽、責任和尊重{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}They taught me the values of honor,  duty and respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}也迷惑我，試圖擊垮我  大四的時候差點把我退學{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}They also hazed me, tried to break me,  and senior year, nearly expelled me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}因為我去當參議員競選志工  導致成績下滑{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}when I volunteered for a Senate race  and my studies suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但這沒阻止他們在30年後{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But that didn't stop them  from soliciting a hefty sum
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}來向我募款興建新圖書館{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}for their new library 30 years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在權力和金錢的影響下  壞成績很快就被遺忘了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How quickly poor grades are forgotten  in the shadow of power and wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你的酒才半滿，法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Your drink is only about half as full  as it should be, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你想把我灌醉嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Are you trying to get me drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}醉倒在水溝裏  這樣我才能偷走你老婆{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Drunk, passed out in the gutter  so I can steal your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你有收到關於  步槍兵的電子郵件嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Did you get the email about the Riflemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}什麼電子郵件？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What email?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我辦公室發的邀請函  我本來希望能看到他們{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}From my office. About the invitations.  I was hoping they would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我再查一下名單  但我不記得有電子郵件…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll check the list,  but I don't remember any email...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒關係，我只是好奇而已{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, not a problem. I was just wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，對不起…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Shit, Frank, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}別想太多{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Don't you sweat it for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你現在就可以補償我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}In fact, here's how you can make it up to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 幫我把酒倒滿  - 沒問題{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-freshen my drink.  -That I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}恭喜你，議員{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Congratulations, Congressman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}瑞米，很高興在這裏見到你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Remy, nice to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}蓋瑞和善可工業的人  要我問候你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Gerry and all the folks at SanCorp  give you their regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}真遺憾他們不能來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, I'm sorry they couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}克萊兒呢？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Where's Claire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她在附近拒絕她的仰慕者{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She's here somewhere, fending off admirers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}善可工業對於  她謝絕捐款的事很失望{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}SanCorp was very disappointed  she turned down their donation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我想也是{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們對於彼得魯索  競選州長也有顧慮{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And they're also concerned  about Peter Russo running for governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你怎麼知道？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now, how do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}四分之三個賓州  都在馬塞勒斯頁岩上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Three-quarters of Pennsylvania  sits on top of the Marcellus Shale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果我連誰要選州長都不知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If I can't find out  who's running for governor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那我根本不配領薪水{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't deserve a dime  of what they're paying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭斯安德沃圖書館{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This Watershed Bill Russo sponsors  places a lot of restrictions on drilling...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}魯索支持的分水嶺提案  在鑽井方面設置很多限制…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}瑞米，國會現在休會  這週末也不談工作{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Remy, Congress is in recess  and this weekend is not about work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}抱歉，你說的有道理{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I apologize, you are absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 善可工業是你唯一的客戶嗎？  - 我有很多客戶{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-ls SanCorp your only account?  -I have plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但別的客戶沒贊助你的圖書館  也沒出我的機票錢{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But my other clients didn't pay for  your library, or my plane ticket down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一次難得的觀光機會  希望你喜歡這裏的景色{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yes, nice little junket for you.  I do hope you're taking in the sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不是第一次來查爾斯頓{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This isn't my first trip to Charleston.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但我相信是第一次  不以我的新聞秘書身份來吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I'll bet it's your first time  not as my Press Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}今晚還要見誰？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Who else you have coming in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不想讓今晚太忙{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I didn't want to pack tonight too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這種酒會常是  為了你這種金主辦的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You know, these receptions are usually  just for the money people, like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一般我會站在這裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Normally, this is where I would start
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}講一些山特諾的歷史  或哲學之類的廢話…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}to drone on about the Sentinel's history,  its philosophy, its yadda, yadda, yadda...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但這些話  我要留到明天演講時說{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I'm gonna save that  for my big speech tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}免得你們要無聊兩次{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and that way I'm not gonna  bore y'all to tears twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}今晚我們邀請到這位  不用我介紹的人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Tonight we're gonna turn it over  to a man who needs no introduction,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}因為我們都知道他這小賤人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}'cause we all know  what a son of a bitch he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}說真的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Seriously, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭安德沃  是我們教導學生德行的榜樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Frank Underwood exemplifies all the virtues  we try to instill in our graduates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，很榮幸能稱你為校友{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We're so proud to call you  an alumnus, Frank,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}把你的名字  永遠留在我們校園裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and to have your name  as a permanent fixture on our campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭安德沃議員{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Congressman Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謝謝，希更斯校長{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you, President Higgins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我要先感謝善可工業{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I first want to thank SanCorp Industries
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們提供資金  實現新圖書館的想法{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}for providing the funds  to make the library possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我剛入學時{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When I matriculated here as a young cadet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}吉米卡特剛當選總統{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Jimmy Carter had just been  elected President.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我畢業時{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}After I graduated,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我和吉米有同樣的願望  希望能再待四年{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I wished that I could have had  another four years, just like Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們兩人都未能如願  但我帶著美好回憶畢業{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, neither of us got our wish,  but I left this campus with fond memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我第一次…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The first time I ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我有收到你的電子郵件{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I got your damn email.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這燈閃多久了？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How long has that light been like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:06:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}大概一個月了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't know. A month, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒人來修嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And nobody's come to fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這裏不會有人來修東西{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Nobody don't fix nothing around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你有叫人修嗎？  - 我在看電視{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Well have you asked?  -I'm watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}別管了，我習慣了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Leave it alone. I'm used to it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 好多了吧？  - 現在太暗了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Better, huh?  -Now it's too dark.
