Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我只想先提醒你  以免你嚇一跳{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I just wanted to give you a heads up,  so it doesn't catch you off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我早就不看新聞了，都是垃圾{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't watch the news no more.  Bunch of garbage.
