Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有看到天花板上的裂痕嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You see that crack up in the ceiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我以前每晚都盯著它入睡{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I used to fall asleep staring at it every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}對它瞭若指掌{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know every inch and curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這裏好暗，我怕黑！{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's dark in here. I'm scared of the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}走開！{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 小心！  - 賭注很大{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Hey, hey!  -Big fucking gamble, my man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}光來了！{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let there be light!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你在想什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:21:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你和法蘭怎麼沒有小孩？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How come you and Frank  have never had kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你也沒有小孩  - 但我沒結婚{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-You've never had kids.  -Yeah, but I'm not married.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}回答問題{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是我們決定的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We just decided not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒有討論很久{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There wasn't some big conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我覺得你在說謊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think you're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}隨你怎麼想{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Think whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你真的沒想過嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You honestly never thought about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有過一兩次吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I mean, yeah, maybe once or twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不覺得遺憾{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I mean, I don't feel there's some void.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒有小孩我也很幸福{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm perfectly happy without.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你呢？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你能想像我  幫小孩擦屁股、換尿布嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Can you imagine me wiping a baby's ass  and changing nappies?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不能{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}其實我剛想像了一下  我得掛電話了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Actually, yes, I just did,  I'm going to have to get off the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那畫面太糟了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You've ruined everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}真的該掛了  已經講一個多小時了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We really should get off.  It's been over an hour I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}掛吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Go on then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我現在就掛  - 我先掛{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I'm hanging up right now.  -No, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 衝啊，肯  - 衝啊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Yeah! Let's go, Ken, let's go.  -Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.73,0:22:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}加油，別放棄{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah, come on. Giddy up, come on.  Don't quit on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 不知道數幾下了  - 加油，別放棄{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I lost count.  -Come on, don't quit on me. Don't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}天啊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你贏了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但這不公平{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But it's not a fair fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你開泛舟公司  我整天坐在辦公桌前{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You run a rafting company.  I sit behind a desk all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}很想看你拿著槳  劃過四級激流的樣子{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'd love to see your ass with a paddle  bouncing through a class-four rapid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果我能讓國會屈服  一點小激流算不上什麼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If I can whip Congress into submission,  I'm not afraid of a little white water.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你無法馴服激流的，法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You can't tame a rapid, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我心跳得好快  我如果心臟病發是你害的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}My heart is beating so fast.  If I have a heart attack it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我的也是{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}摸摸看{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我需要再喝一杯{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I need another drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我也是{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think I'll have another, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}別喝光了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Don't bogart that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這個地方造就我們嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you think this place made us?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:23:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}什麼意思？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.25,0:24:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我今天走過校園時在想  這裏有意義嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When I walked on campus today I wondered,  did it mean anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這只是我們生活四年的地方  還有更深的意義嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If it's just a place we spent four years  of our lives or was there more?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但我知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I do know you were always the guy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.40,0:24:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}會有建築物以你命名{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}who was going to get  a building named after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當我看到你罵那個訓練中士  就知道了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I knew that the moment I saw you  cuss out the drill sergeant
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.50,0:24:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們當時還是小毛頭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}when we were knobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.44,0:24:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}圖書館是個騙局{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The library is a sham.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}希更斯找我幫忙  我找別人幫忙{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Higgins asked me a favor,  I asked someone else a favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.68,0:24:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們就把我的名字放上去了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}they slapped my name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.48,0:24:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}政治跟其他事情都一樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Politics. Like everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.35,0:24:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不是每個人都能幫這種忙{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not everybody gets asked those favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.88,0:24:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}或是知道怎麼達成{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Or knows how to deliver on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.52,0:24:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}50年後，他們就會換掉匾額{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}In 50 years, they'll just replace it  with something else,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.92,0:24:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就像他們把我換掉一樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}just like they're doing with this for mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.89,0:24:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你還是有建樹，不管維持多久{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You still built something.  However long it lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.79,0:24:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}圖書館不重要{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The library doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但我希望這個地方有意義{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I want to think that this place did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.43,0:24:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}對當年的我們意義深遠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think it meant a lot to us, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.04,0:24:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那我們呢？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And what about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.78,0:25:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}老實說，我沒想那麼多{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Honestly, I haven't really  thought about it that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.98,0:25:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}都是陳年往事了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.32,0:25:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們之前那麼親密{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We were so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.69,0:25:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}像兄弟一樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Like brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.85,0:25:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}比兄弟更親{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}More than brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.32,0:25:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們只是孩子，法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We were kids, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.52,0:25:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}胡搞了幾次{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We messed around a couple of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.39,0:25:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我深深被你吸引…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I was so drawn to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.26,0:25:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我總是能逗你笑{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I could always make you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.17,0:25:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們怎麼會失去連絡？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How did we lose touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.74,0:25:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你進了法學院，我去從軍{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You went to law school. I joined the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.07,0:25:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你去競選議員  我搬去科羅拉多州{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You ran for Congress. I moved to Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.31,0:25:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}30年過去了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thirty years goes by.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.91,0:25:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我的孩子都比我們當年大了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I got children older than we were back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.12,0:25:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，你有對象嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you have anyone, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.12,0:25:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我有克萊兒{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I have Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.89,0:25:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}除了她之外{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Besides Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.72,0:25:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有時候有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I have, from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.93,0:25:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果我要誰，就會得到{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If I want someone, I want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.43,0:25:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是吸引力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.24,0:26:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你能快樂我就快樂，法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It made me happy to make you happy, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.94,0:26:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒什麼不好的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Didn't see any harm in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.31,0:26:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}知道我為何喜歡泛舟？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You know why I love rafting?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.34,0:26:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在水上的時候{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When you're on the water,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.61,0:26:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你只會想著眼前的一切{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}all you're thinking about  is what's right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.48,0:26:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一切都在當下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Everything is in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.48,0:26:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我沒時間去想過去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't really have time  to think about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.93,0:26:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你對我意義重大{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You meant something to me.
