Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.38,0:28:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們用來命名圖書館的  那個人是誰？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Who is he that they're  naming the place after?
