Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.81,0:29:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒有我不能應付的事  去休息一下吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, nothing I can't handle. Go get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.65,0:29:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你厲害嗎？  - 還不錯{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Were you good?  -Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.06,0:29:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不是先發球員  但還是有常上場{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I wasn't a starter,  but I got my time on the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.79,0:29:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你長大後比較性感{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think you look sexier now, all grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.76,0:29:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}議員？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Congressman?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.17,0:29:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們準備好了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We're ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.70,0:30:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你說兩年{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You said two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.13,0:30:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我相信兩年是合理的評估{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah, I think two years is a realistic estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.54,0:30:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 如果有通過的話  - 我相信會的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-If it passes at all.  -Which I think it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.74,0:30:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}相信還是知道？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You think or you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.74,0:30:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不敢說百分之百  但我有信心{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I can't predict 100%, but I'm confident it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.91,0:30:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你相信，你有信心  你不敢說百分之百{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You think, you're confident,  you can't predict 100%,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.61,0:30:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}對我們有幫助嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}how does any of that help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.85,0:30:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我告訴你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll tell you something,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.11,0:30:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我百分之百付不出房貸{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm 100% unable  to pay my mortgage right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.15,0:30:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我百分之百沒辦法  幫我孩子買文具{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm 100% unable to buy  my kids school supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.65,0:30:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們該靠先生的殘障津貼  過日子嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We supposed to live off  my husband's disability?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.06,0:30:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}會有支薪的訓練課程{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There'll be paid training programs available.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.52,0:30:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}薪水多少？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How much will they pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.33,0:30:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}比你們在造船廠的工資少{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Granted, it's less than you made  at the shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.40,0:30:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 多少？  - 一小時六塊錢{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-So how much?  -It's about $6 an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.37,0:30:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}還不到最低工資{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's not even minimum wage.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.57,0:31:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 放屁，魯索！  - 你們要把這當成投資{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Horseshit, Russo!  -You have to see it as an investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.67,0:31:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}訓練課程也是珍貴資源…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The training programs  are a valuable resource...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.37,0:31:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你沒聽懂{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You're not getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.64,0:31:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我沒辦法投資{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I can't afford to make investments.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.04,0:31:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一小時六塊錢  等於叫我全家流落街頭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}$6 an hour puts my family on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.71,0:31:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你要我打五份工嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What, do you want me to work five jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.98,0:31:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果你們有一份兼職  加上訓練課程…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If you get a part-time job,  that and the training program...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.18,0:31:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}想知道我的想法嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You want to know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.55,0:31:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你坐在華府  想出一堆漂亮數字的提案{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think you sit around in Washington  coming up with all sorts of fancy numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.46,0:31:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}都是紙上談兵  但對我們都沒有幫助{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and solutions that look good on paper,  but that doesn't cut it for the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.73,0:31:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你說過支持我們，說謊！{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You said you had our backs,  you lying piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.63,0:31:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}紙不能吃，也不能遮風避雨{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We don't eat paper for dinner.  You can't put a paper roof over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.74,0:31:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們投票給你的時候{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When we all voted for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.67,0:31:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒想到這些選票  都是我們自己棺材上的釘子{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I didn't think that every one of those votes  was another nail in our own coffins.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.04,0:31:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}拜託大家坐下，十分鐘就好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Please, everybody,  just sit down for 10 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.68,0:31:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們能逐項討論這個提案{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}we can go over this proposal point-by-point.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.32,0:31:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這樣你們就會  有足夠的資訊和資源…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And you can get the information you need  to get the resources that you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.16,0:31:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 他們好像不想解決  - 他們是害怕{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-It's like they don't want to find a solution.  -They're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.36,0:31:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我知道他們害怕  但不表示不能聽你說…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I understand that they're scared,  but that doesn't mean they can't listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.36,0:32:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不瞭解他們，克裏絲汀娜{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You don't know these people, Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.26,0:32:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我替你工作三年了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I worked in your office for three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.13,0:32:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我跟他們講話，接他們的電話  回他們的郵件…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I spoke to them, I took their calls,  I replied to their emails...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.10,0:32:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你沒有和他們一起長大{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You didn't grow up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.67,0:32:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不需要和他們一起長大  才能同情他們的處境…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't need to grow up hand-to-mouth  to empathize with the fact that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.24,0:32:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們不需要同情{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}They're not interested in empathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.15,0:32:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}房間鑰匙在我外套裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The house keys are in my jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.25,0:32:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我再打給你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.92,0:32:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 彼得  - 我說我會再打給你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Peter.  -I said I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.39,0:32:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}寫功課之類的…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do your homework or Sister Mary Joseph...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.89,0:32:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你根本沒做…別騙我  我以前用一樣的藉口騙我父母{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You didn't do it... Don't lie to me.  I used to use the same ploy with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.33,0:32:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}胡扯{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Baloney.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.70,0:32:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}寫完功課再吃飯{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We do the homework,  and then we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.54,0:32:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}誰餓了？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Who's hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.07,0:32:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你們想吃什麼？  - 漢堡{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-What do you guys want?  -Hamburger.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.88,0:32:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 披薩  - 不行{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Pizza.  -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.41,0:32:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不吃披薩，你們每天都…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No pizza, you guys can eat that every...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.85,0:32:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}親愛的，帶孩子們上樓{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Sweetheart, take the kids upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.13,0:33:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你怎麼進來的？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How'd you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.16,0:33:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你還是把鑰匙  放在門廊的鬆動磚頭後面{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You still keep the spare key behind  the loose brick on the porch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.36,0:33:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你闖進我家？  那樣嚇壞我的孩子？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You break into my house?  You scare my kids like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.93,0:33:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我們得談談，保羅  - 昨晚談過了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-We gotta talk, Paul.  -We talked last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.77,0:33:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}馬上滾{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.90,0:33:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我可以說服他們  但我需要你的幫忙{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I can convince these people,  but I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.87,0:33:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 離開我家  - 坐下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Leave my house.  -Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.01,0:33:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我孩子在樓上  我不想打你，彼得{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't want to have to hurt you  with my children upstairs, Petey.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.24,0:33:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那就幫我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Then help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.35,0:33:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}最後一次機會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.48,0:33:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不走{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.36,0:33:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}回樓上！{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Get back upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.26,0:34:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們在做什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.63,0:34:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不想跟你打架，彼得{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't want to fight you, Petey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.90,0:34:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我也不想{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't want to fight you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.10,0:34:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我可以，但我們不需要這樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I will, but we don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.84,0:34:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你要我做什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.98,0:34:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你們選我來代表你們  但我無法阻止不可避免的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You elected me to represent you.  But I couldn't forestall the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.22,0:34:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}造船廠關閉了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The shipyard was closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.02,0:34:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就算今年不關，明後年也會關  我們心知肚明{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If not this year, then next, or the year after.  We all know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.09,0:34:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我可以騙你們  我可以假裝多做一些事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I could have lied to you.  I could have pretended to do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.73,0:34:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但我不想活在過去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I don't believe in living in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.66,0:34:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我只關心未來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I only care about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.40,0:34:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}接下來的事實可能不好聽…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Here's another truth  that's gonna be hard to swallow...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.47,0:34:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你們只能靠我了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm all you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.07,0:35:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}華府沒人管你們的死活{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Nobody in Washington gives  a fuck about you. No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.51,0:35:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他說得對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.01,0:35:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不管你們對彼得有何想法  我們不跟著他，就一無所有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Whatever you think of Petey,  we either go with him or we got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.32,0:35:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我的提議符合  你們的需要或標準嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now does what I'm offering you come  anywhere near what you want or deserve?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.42,0:35:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.52,0:35:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但你們得睜大雙眼  把握眼前的東西{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But you gotta open your eyes  and take what's in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.39,0:35:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們能慢慢發展{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We can build on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.63,0:35:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}五千份工作變成一萬  然後變成一萬五千{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}5,000 jobs becomes 10, then 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.43,0:35:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這不會一夕成真  但總比什麼都不做來得好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not in the snap of a finger,  but faster than doing nothing will.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.77,0:35:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我可以指望你們嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Can I count on all ofyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.45,0:35:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我就當你們答應了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}All right, I'll take that as a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.39,0:35:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們要你們的連絡方式{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We'll need your contact information,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.82,0:35:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}才能把資料傳給你們  分享給朋友{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}so we can send you materials  to share with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.43,0:35:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在討論資金要怎麼引入{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now, let's talk about the way  the money's gonna get phased in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.96,0:35:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}總共有六階段，第一階段…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's gonna happen in six stages. Stage one...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.22,0:36:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}左轉，齊步走{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Left face, forward march.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.30,0:36:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭斯安德沃的職業生涯  哈佛法學院{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Francis Underwood's career,  Harvard Law degree,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.24,0:36:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}南卡羅來納州史上  最年輕的州議員之一{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}one of the youngest state legislators  in the history of South Carolina,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.14,0:36:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}美國國會22年的資深議員{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}a 22-year veteran of the U.S. Congress,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.95,0:36:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}眾議院多數黨黨鞭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}House Majority Whip,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.41,0:36:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}充分證明年輕人  在山特諾學到的價值觀{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}speaks volumes about the values  young people learn here at the Sentinel,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.25,0:36:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}像是榮譽、責任、紀律{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}values like honor, duty, discipline,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.26,0:37:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}犧牲、服務和尊敬{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Iike sacrifice, service and respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.80,0:37:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}女士先生們  法蘭斯安德沃圖書館{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Ladies and Gentlemen,  the Francis J. Underwood library.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.12,0:37:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}議員？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Congressman?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.29,0:37:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謝謝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.30,0:37:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我寫了一段演講稿{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I wrote a speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.23,0:37:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但我不打算念{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I'm not gonna read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.41,0:37:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒有什麼是永恆的  這棟建築物也一樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Nothing is permanent.  Not even this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.54,0:37:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我無意顯得忘恩負義{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't mean to sound ungrateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.48,0:37:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我很感恩，也非常榮幸{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I am very grateful, I'm deeply honored,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.85,0:37:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}非常感動{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and I am very moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.13,0:38:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我這週末有幸  能和一群朋友一起度過{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I had the good fortune of spending most  of this weekend with a group of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.17,0:38:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一群好久不見的老友{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Friends I haven't seen in a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.24,0:38:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一群我在這裏交的朋友{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Friends I made here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.61,0:38:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}大部分的年輕學生  可能不知道我是誰{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Most of you young cadets  probably don't know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.58,0:38:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只是政客  一個有少數成就的名字{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Politician. A name. A few accomplishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.19,0:38:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但我不怪你們{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.45,0:38:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我和你們一樣大的時候{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When I was your age, why,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.19,0:38:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我也不太在乎  那些老頭子做過什麼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I didn't care much for what  men in gray hair did
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.13,0:38:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}或是要說什麼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}or what they had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.77,0:38:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我希望我能形容…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I wish I could describe...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.48,0:39:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}和諧  這個詞在我腦中揮之不去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Harmony.  That's the word that's stuck in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.49,0:39:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}和諧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.86,0:39:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這和永恆的事物無關{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's not about what's lasting or permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.66,0:39:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}而是個人的聲音{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It is about individual voices
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.70,0:39:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在一瞬間集結在一起{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}coming together for a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.44,0:39:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那一瞬間{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and that moment lasts
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.34,0:39:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只有一口氣那麼長{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}the length of a breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.85,0:39:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這就是我對這個地方的感覺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's what I think about my time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.59,0:39:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}請原諒我  我昨晚多喝了幾杯威士忌{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You'll have to forgive me.  I had more than a few whiskeys last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.56,0:39:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當我還是學生  我們可以喝整晚的酒{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You know, when I was a cadet,  we could drink all night,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.66,0:39:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}然後早上起來行軍30公里{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}then get up in the morning  and march 20 miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.40,0:39:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在能走上這三階樓梯  就不錯了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but these days I'm lucky  I got up these three steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.74,0:39:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}非常感謝你們{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I want to thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.37,0:39:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是至高的榮耀{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This is a great honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.97,0:40:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}感謝希更斯校長{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I want to thank President Higgins,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.31,0:40:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當然還有我此生的摯愛  克萊兒{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and of course, the love of my life, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.08,0:40:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謝謝各位{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you all very much.
